{
  "id": "RAW_22c8ef",
  "title": "TextFlux 重磅发布：告别复杂控制信号！多语种高保真场景文本编辑新时代",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3Njc0NTgwMg==&mid=2247503491&idx=1&sn=94972b8b0d82197532d6bdcfedd2ed42",
  "date": "2025-09-19 04:07:00",
  "author": "哔哩哔哩技术",
  "siteName": "哔哩哔哩技术",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=007003d4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F1BMf5Ir754R8pW8GV1DmzKsvuyLCBpdViblsV80ygZjdYzFdYowDurSLrpo8TWjGicLDfCxd4qxfjjoSNHfRYP6A%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding-left: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(0, 0, 0);padding-left: 5px;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">前言</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 0px 15px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在文本编辑领域，设想一种技术：无需复杂控制信号，只靠字形图像和少量训练数据，就能把文字“无缝”嵌入真实场景——中文招牌、日文海报、韩文标语，多语言统统适用。这就是 TextFlux 带来的全新体验，由bilibili人工智能平台部，联合北京大学王选所提出。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">TextFlux 不再依赖 OCR 编码器和繁复的监督信号，而是把渲染好的字形直接贴进场景，让模型型专注学习“如何与周围环境自然融合”。思路直观，架构简洁，却能生成更真实、更快捷、更通用的多语言场景文本编辑效果。相关代码、权重和数据集均已开源。截至目前，该项目</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">已支持ComfyUI，能够在消费级显卡上部署和运行</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100019831\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3462963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f55bf61f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F1BMf5Ir754R8pW8GV1DmzKsvuyLCBpdV7icVFMQmZtwyUOQmjpsa68KaiacynASm0riaDHKqHA7Sy1Qve8o75FsVg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">图1 TextFlux项目开源页面</span></sup></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding-left: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(0, 0, 0);padding-left: 5px;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">相关链接</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 0px 15px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">代码：</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0,0,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/yyyyyxie/textflux\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/yyyyyxie/textflux</a></span></em></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 0px 15px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">权重：</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0,0,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/yyyyyxie/textflux\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/yyyyyxie/textflux</a></span></em></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 0px 15px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">demo页面：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://yyyyyxie.github.io/textflux-site/\" target=\"_blank\">https://yyyyyxie.github.io/textflux-site/</a></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">ComfyUI：</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0,0,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/yyyyyxie/textflux_comfyui\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/yyyyyxie/textflux_comfyui</a></span></em></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p></p>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding-left: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(0, 0, 0);padding-left: 5px;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">背景介绍</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">场景文本编辑需兼顾两方面：一是文本“拼写”精确性，二是与场景视觉的自然融合。传统方法虽强化拼写，却容易产生“贴片”感；或者反之，虽融合逼真，但文本识别失败。借助扩散模型（DiT）优越的上下文推理能力，TextFlux 摒弃了传统方法基于 OCR 编码器的复杂条件注入，将渲染的字形图像与场景图像在空间维度融合，转而让模型专注于“如何将字形自然融入场景”，而非“如何认识文字”。在</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">多行生成和单行生成领域</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，TextFlux都有不俗的表现。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;text-align: center;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">多行生成</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">TextFlux能够一次性编辑生成多行文本，每一行文字的内容、位置和风格都可以精准调整，文字与场景无缝融合，既真实又具有可读性。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;text-align: center;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">关键特征</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 0px 15px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">OCR‑Free 架构：简化模型结构，无需 OCR 编码器。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 0px 15px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">高保真 &amp; 上下文风格一致：渲染精准，风格与场景浑然一体。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 0px 15px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">多语种 &amp; 低资源适配能力：优异的多语言兼容力，新增语言仅需极少样本（如少于 1,000 条）即可快速适配。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 0px 15px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">零样本泛化能力：对训练集中未出现的字符也能准确渲染</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 0px 15px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">可控的多行文本生成：灵活合成多行文本，可逐行精确控制排版与内容。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">数据高效：仅使用其他方法约百分之一的数据量，即可完成训练。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p></p>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;text-align: center;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">单行生成</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">针对多行一次性生成时存在小文本生成效果不佳的问题，考虑到单行文本编辑是许多用户的核心使用场景，并且往往能产生更稳定、更高质量的结果。团队发布了针对该场景优化的beta 版权重模型。与原始模型在整幅全尺寸掩码上渲染字形不同，beta 版本采用单行图像条作为字形条件输入。这种方式既减少了不必要的计算开销，又能提供更加稳定且高质量的监督信号，从而直接提升单行和小字体文本的渲染效果。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;text-align: center;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">关键特征</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 0px 15px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">显著提升单行文本渲染质量。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 0px 15px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">单行文本推理速度提升约 1.4 倍。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">大幅提高小尺寸文本的合成准确性。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p></p>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding-left: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(0, 0, 0);padding-left: 5px;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">效果展示</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;text-align: center;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">出色的多语言编辑能力</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">TextFlux 在多语种场景文本编辑任务中表现优异，能够高质量生成不同语言的文本，满足多元化视觉场景编辑需求。即便是新加入的低资源语言，只需</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">少于 1,000 条样本</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，TextFlux 也可迅速适配并生成高质量文本，极大降低了数据标注和获取门槛。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100019833\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5694444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5ce66ce9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F1BMf5Ir754R8pW8GV1DmzKsvuyLCBpdVE4Mk9DLD8ib8YaNrMb5meKH7Kdf8S9HP1iaG4KajWKjlLABEQ3nNuTicA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">图2 TextFlux编辑多语言场景文本</span></sup></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;text-align: center;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">优越的视觉保真度和文本准确性</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在视觉保真度和文本准确性两个方面，TextFlux 在定量评测和定性对比中均优于现有SOTA的文本编辑方法。尤其对于低分辨率的输入图像，TextFlux能够自适应的生成相对更清晰的文本。在一次性多行生成和单行生成的场景下，TextFlux都具有不俗的表现。甚至在和目前参数量十倍于己的基于LLM的图像生成模型相比较也取得了可比的效果。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;text-align: center;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">与已有基于Diffusion方法的比较</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100019835\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6416667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a931174f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F1BMf5Ir754R8pW8GV1DmzKsvuyLCBpdVyBUQYibepgjmKtPEvrrIUuaQA3ia7uuH4DOarwebZGic19JPS6J5KXPTg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">图3 TextFlux与已有基于扩散模型的文字编辑方法的比较</span></sup></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;text-align: center;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">与目前基于LLM的文生图模型的比较</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100019834\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df2ea6b7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F1BMf5Ir754R8pW8GV1DmzKsvuyLCBpdVQgKKYT3WNk6icVibjUj2awDsibxLF0JW2IiaVGk1DiayPUVQUO3p867vdnw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">图4 TextFlux与已有基于LLM的文字编辑方法的比较</span></sup></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;text-align: center;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">可扩展性及Zero-Shot能力</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">得益于其创新的 OCR-Free 架构与视觉融合机制，TextFlux 对训练集中未包含的字符也能实现即时渲染（zero‑shot），有效拓展了应用场景。目前对于训练集中未见到的生僻中文字符及横排小语种，TextFlux有很好的泛化能力。尽管在未经特别挑选的情况下，个别字符有概率出现错误，但依旧证明了架构在OOD问题上强大的泛化能力。值得注意的是，目前生成连笔文字如阿拉伯文上，TextFlux的能力受限，这也是本工作将来的优化和研究方向之一。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100019832\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9e098105&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F1BMf5Ir754R8pW8GV1DmzKsvuyLCBpdVcPZDRgP4XRQIv51ibymVibB3DVCNViayOVpttJmTV9mez8MVaITlxIdbQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">图5 TextFlux在未见字集和未见语言上的Zero-shot能力</span></sup></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100019839\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3546296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=89272108&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F1BMf5Ir754R8pW8GV1DmzKsvuyLCBpdVMk40Y88IzK5tv3mHtiaGhWibRfkdkowyc3poN9iaZXSGepgiaF6UPSYuhA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">图6 TextFlux生成连笔文字的能力尚有待加强</span></sup></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;text-align: center;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">保留原始基座的通用能力</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，TextFlux不会改变原本基座模型的通用能力，具备良好的可扩展性，基于提供的权重，能够赋予其他基于该基座模型的工作多语言的生成能力。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100019837\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0583333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a13945c8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F1BMf5Ir754R8pW8GV1DmzKsvuyLCBpdVE4OZMAovfVGq0rGRdKWw7kV8lPhaST3EAjLSEen9kx13Fibiaiblqy1Jw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">图7 TextFlux很好的保留了Flux-Fill的通用能力</span></sup></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding-left: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(0, 0, 0);padding-left: 5px;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(12, 182, 242);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">总结</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">TextFlux 打破了场景文本编辑的瓶颈，提出一种“OCR-Free”架构：只用字形图像作引导，依托 Diffusion Transformer（DiT）完成生成。相比需要额外视觉-文本控制模块和海量标注的方法，它结构更精简、数据效率更高，支持多语种、多行文本及复杂字形，甚至对未见字符也能零样本泛化。这一新范式不仅提升了视觉真实度和文字准确率，也为多语言文本融合落地提供了可行路径。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 0px 15px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">-End-</span></p>\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者丨seasonxy、墨枢、Jerry酱</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "TextFlux 发布多语种高保真场景文本编辑技术，通过创新的 OCR-Free 架构，实现无需复杂控制信号，仅靠字形图像即可将文字无缝嵌入真实场景，并已开源支持消费级显卡部署。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "TextFlux 发布多语种高保真场景文本编辑技术，通过创新的 OCR-Free 架构，实现无需复杂控制信号，仅靠字形图像即可将文字无缝嵌入真实场景，并已开源支持消费级显卡部署。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了 Bilibili 人工智能平台部与北京大学王选所联合提出的 TextFlux 场景文本编辑技术。该技术摒弃了传统方法对 OCR 编码器和复杂监督信号的依赖，创新性地采用“OCR-Free”架构，依托 Diffusion Transformer (DiT)，直接将渲染好的字形图像与场景图像融合，使模型专注于学习文字如何自然融入周围环境。TextFlux 在多行和单行文本生成方面均表现出色，具有高保真度、上下文风格一致性、优异的多语种及低资源适配能力（仅需少量样本），并支持零样本泛化。与现有 SOTA 扩散模型及基于 LLM 的图像生成模型相比，TextFlux 在视觉保真度和文本准确性上均显示出优势，尤其在低分辨率和小尺寸文本处理上效果显著。该项目已开源代码、权重和数据集，并支持 ComfyUI，可在消费级显卡上运行，极大降低了技术门槛和应用成本。",
